snippet.title: DoYouFeelLucky
snippet.description:
I like to play around with music, video editing and ideas. You can help support this work by buying me a coffee: http://ko-fi.com/doyoufeellucky

E-mail: doyoufeellucky@gmail.com

Any videos which may be blocked are viewable under paid subscription here: https://vimeo.com/user16251575

These videos are made purely for the joy of it, this account is not and cannot be monetized and all video edits are absolutely not for profit. All copyrighted materials are credited to their rightful owners.
